                    <p class="book-authors">Authors: Donald Trump, Stanislav Caragheaur</p>
                    <p class="book-summary">Summary: hehehe hohoho</p>
                    <p class="book-publisher">Publisher: McGraw-Hill, New York</p>
                </div>
            </div>
